OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FQuite cloudy
OL,6,Fthrough the evening and overnight with
OL,7,Fsome showery rain, heavy at times.
OL,8,FSome drier and clearer spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping towards morning. Windy at
OL,10,Ftimes.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FA dry, bright start in the
OL,13,Feast, becoming cloudy through the
OL,14,Fmorning with patchy rain. Cloudy with
OL,15,Foccasionally heavy rain in west.
OL,16,FBecoming dry with clear spells in
OL,17,Fevening. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
